vyges-power computes per-instance leakage and dynamic (switching) power from a
gate-level netlist + Liberty + an activity source (VCD/SAIF or vectorless), and
emits the per-instance activity/current map that vyges-em-ir consumes — closing
the char -> power -> em-ir power-integrity loop.

Per-foundry calibration data and plugins, where applicable, are distributed
separately under their own terms and are not part of this repository.
